snippet.title: Fantasy Life - Overview Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Fantasy Life arrives 26 September 2014 on Nintendo 3DS. Find out about all the things you can do in the game!
Fantasy Life is available to pre-order here: http://ow.ly/AlRcC

Age Rating: PEGI 7 (http://www.pegi.info)
Facebook Nintendo 3DS: https://facebook.com/Nintendo3DSuk
Facebook Wii U: https://www.facebook.com/WiiU.co.uk
Twitter Nintendo UK: https://twitter.com/NintendoUK
YouTube Nintendo UK: http://ow.ly/pcJxF
